text: American weapons, self weapons, County weapons, Enemy of America's weapons, War weapons and other weapons that were sold to by "Robert" who is an American citizen." As the line goes: it is a crime for any one to possess or sell any weapon in a county. A missile is a weapon that is not a missile but also comes into the category of weapons." In the first half of the quote, we are told about Robert's criminal act of selling weapons. The quote then refers to the above list of weapons and informs us that these weapons are illegal to possess or sell in any county. It suggests that anyone found with these types of weapons will be arrested.
